name: Fuzzys Audio Test
description: Crazy thing happened last night, and thank god I got it on video. I was doing a mandatory test on Fuzzy, and audio test, and it only took one sound to make him freak out! The thing lunged at me and I almost had a heart attack. I will be sure to record the rest of the audio tests with the other animatronics. 5/02/95 - 10 days till opening
